Package GUI.listeners

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttackActorListener
    Listen the attack button and creates a battle on click.
    BattleActionListener
    Class for all listeners of BattleActions buttons which are created on start of a battle in the BattlePanel.
    ChangeLanguageListener
    Listen the change language buttons.
    FoundItemsListener
    Listens the resume button when finding items.
    GoToMainMenuListener
    Listener which only sets the game back into main menu.
    MainMenuQuitListener
    Listen quit game button on main menu.
    MainMenuStartListener
    Listen start game button on main menu.
    MoveToListener
    Listen the move button on main panel.
    PlayerNameListener
    Listens startgame button on player creation.
    SetPlayerCountListener
    On click starts creates the PlayerNamePanel, and gives the JSpinner value as parameter.
    SettingsListener
    Listens settings button.
    TurnBeginListener
    Listen start turn button.
    TurnEndListener
    Listen to the ok button in the moveresult panel.
